descriptionHtml:
Makes Brelyna prettier and stronger. Brelyna no longer uses conjuration so her pesky atronochs will no longer get in the way of your spells. However her destruction skills are improved and she is more durable. 

I always liked Brelyna but her atronochs always seemed to get in my way and while getting rid of that I thought i\'d make her better looking and share it just incase anyone else felt the same way.
author: Crayolacrayon
